## Import

App Service Plan instances can be imported using the `resource id`, e.g.

```sh
 $ codeinfra import azure:appservice/plan:Plan instance1 /subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/resourceGroups/mygroup1/providers/Microsoft.Web/serverfarms/instance1
```

azure:appservice/slot:Slot.description:
Manages an App Service Slot (within an App Service).

> **Note:** When using Slots - the `app_settings`, `connection_string` and `site_config` blocks on the `azure.appservice.AppService` resource will be overwritten when promoting a Slot using the `azure.appservice.ActiveSlot` resource.


